# Robocopy Sync ŌĆö mosc-temp ŌåÆ test-site + template

## **Overview**

Use when the user asks to **mirror `mosc-temp` into** the satellite/test frontends (`event-site-front-end-test-site`, `event-site-front-end-template`) via **`robocopy`**, then **commit and push** the destinations.

**Related rules:**
- [git_local_push.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/git_local_push.mdc) ŌĆö commit/push, secret filter, unstaged files
- [git_pull.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/git_pull.mdc) ŌĆö pull-only (run before commit if branch is behind)
- [deploy_apps_to_amplify_ecs.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/deploy_apps_to_amplify_ecs.mdc) ŌĆö Amplify deploy after push

**Copy-paste user prompt:**

```
robocopy "F:\project_workspace\mosc-temp" "F:\project_workspace\event-site-front-end-test-site" /E /XD .git .claude /XF .env.local .env.production

robocopy "F:\project_workspace\mosc-temp" "F:\project_workspace\event-site-front-end-template" /E /XD .git .claude

Commit and push the destinations.
Follow .cursor/rules/git_robocopy_mosc_sync.mdc
```

