Pushing `event-site-front-end-test-site` **`release/v1.0.0`** may trigger Amplify (`d1502cffqchuun`). Template deploys on **`main`**. For verify steps, see [deploy_apps_to_amplify_ecs.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/deploy_apps_to_amplify_ecs.mdc).

